snippet.title: ✅  Amber Heard 'had pus oozing from scalp wounds' after Johnny Depp 'headbutt'
snippet.description:

💖 Please Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQju4Bo1Tjk9SzhHQDknWaw?sub_confirmation=1
✍  Amber Heard got emotional as she detailed the injuries she claims to have suffered in a fiery row with  at their Los Angeles penthouse - eging she sustained two black eyes, a broken nose and had pus oozing from wounds on her scalp.    Heard, 34, is back at London's High Court for her second day giving evidence in Depp 's libel case against News Group Newspapers.  Depp, 57, is suing NGN over a story published in The Sun in 201 which branded him a "wife beater" - a claim which he strenuously denies.  During today's questioning, Heard was asked about a heated row wit the actor at their home in Los Angeles on December 15 in 2015.  Heard's voice cracked with emotion as she detailed the injuries she clams to have suffered in the argument.  She told the court she had "two black eyes, a broken nose and broken lip, bruises  over my body, bruises on my forearm.  "I think I had bruises on my chin, chunks of my hair were missing, pus was in the wounds on my hairline."  The actress claimed the "re ...
